{"tid":1099923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"壽臣山道東豪宅工人追欠薪 危站天台","createTime":"2019-04-10T05:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T05:54:01.000Z","uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"44fefad31b6b84cbf3195ca4103d197f00eefee7","tid":1099923,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjXhFFn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjXhFFn.png&h=6cc80a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工人追薪在天台徘徊，警員到場了解。胡恩宏攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZnJBdQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZnJBdQ.png&h=e73f9069&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壽臣山道東1號進行翻新工程，全幢搭有棚架。 胡恩宏攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bn9Td0F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbn9Td0F.png&h=e9ad2c2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡恩宏攝<br />\n<br />\n香港仔壽臣山道東1號一列3層高大宅，外牆進行翻新工程，搭有棚架。早上11時26分，住客發現約12名工人，在其中一幢住宅天台危險位置徘徊，報警求助。警員到場了解，工人報稱來自不同工種，遭拖欠薪金三個月，稍後工人聯絡了判頭，雙方達成協議，工人自行返回安全位置，警方列勞資糾紛處理，事件中無人受傷。"},{"pid":"06d78604c6260643c816ee030ae3f7f7c053c337","tid":1099923,"uid":32028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"跳左落黎, 個大宅淨係跌5%, 都唔知唔見幾多錢<br />\n真係幾醒目"}]}